1.11 Color Rules

The website should remain predominantly white.

Green should be used only to highlight important information.

Avoid excessive color usage.

If everything is highlighted, nothing stands out.

1.12 Typography

Preferred font stack:

Inter

Roboto

Open Sans

Arial

sans-serif

